      "heading": "Tổng quan",
      "html": "<p><i><b>Note:</b></i> This guide is based on my experience in the game and may be subjective. -- <a href=\"https://dontstarve.fandom.com/wiki/User:Loopuleasa\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Loopuleasa</a></p>\n<hr>\n\n<p>This is a guide for <a href=\"http://dontstarve.wikia.com/wiki/File:Don&#x27;t_Starve_Together_icon.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"></a> Don&#x27;t Starve Together, that focuses on the optimal strategy for the first 13 days for one player.\n</p><p>This guide resembles a speed-running min-max approach of getting your first base setup as fast as possible, with as many resources as possible, as efficient as possible.\n</p>",
      "id": "overview",
      "level": 1
    }
